  <brief_title>A Two-Arm, Multi-Centre Clinical Evaluation of the xTAG Gastrointestinal Pathogen Panel</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Two-Arm, Multi-Centre Clinical Evaluation of the xTAG Gastrointestinal Pathogen Panel (xTAG GPP) in Patients With Signs and Symptoms of Infectious Colitis and Gastroenteritis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
